                        <h3><a href="#">Availability of Companion Documents</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>This guideline is available as a Personal Digital Assistant (PDA) download via the APPRISOR&trade; Document Viewer from <a href="/web/20180712204054/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=46232&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fwww.apprisor.com%2fwhatsnew.cfm%3fCFID%3d1713610%26CFTOKEN%3d45316293" title="Apprisor Web site">www.apprisor.com</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712204054im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>.</p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Patient Resources</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>None available</p></div></p>
